        return False
    magic_constant = 15
    row1 = sum(square[0:3])
    row2 = sum(square[3:6])
    row3 = sum(square[6:9])
    col1 = sum(square[0::3])
    col2 = sum(square[1::3])
    col3 = sum(square[2::3])
    diag1 = sum(square[0::4])
    diag2 = sum(square[2:7:-2])
    return row1 == row2 == row3 == col1 == col2 == col3 == diag1 == diag2 == magic_constant
